{"TopicId":139713,"ForumId":36,"TopicTitle":"Benji\u0026#039;s Light up Command Pods","CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T00:30:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T00:30:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIntroducing,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:22px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003EBenji\u0027s Light up Command Pods!\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003EThis mod allows you to turn lights on and off on command pods/modules like you can with cockpits!\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003EIt also works on the Hitch-hiker Storage Container. This is good for making your rockets look a lot cooler, as well as being more visible in the dark. This doesn\u0027t currently work for the Mobile Processing Lab but I am working on it.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003EMore info and mod download at\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022http://mods.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal/245069-benjis-light-up-command-pods\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://mods.curse.com/ksp-mods/kerbal/245069-benjis-light-up-command-pods\u003C/a\u003E.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003EThis is the first time I\u0027ve made anything even remotely like a mod so please go easy on me. Thanks to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/109931-ven/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022109931\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/109931-ven/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Ven\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0as most of the files in this mod are based off of his \u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/83696-112-stock-part-revamp-update-192/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EStock Part Revamp\u003C/a\u003E. I\u0027m hoping that overtime I will use more of my stuff.\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003ELicence:\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003EThis work is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License.\u00A0To view a copy of this license, visit\u00A0http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/. Some files and textures are taken from Ven\u0027s Stock Part Revamp. If you like what you see here, I suggest downloading his mod.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:14px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022line-height:25.6px;\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-14T02:30:52Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2016 02:30  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Benji13\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShotgunNinja","CreatedById":159391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T00:34:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMan these lights are very nice!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://media-curse.cursecdn.com/attachments/186/229/a8973eee1707300d50e1b3b8e4c25ade.png\u0022 alt=\u0022a8973eee1707300d50e1b3b8e4c25ade.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T00:35:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks. As I said, most of that is Ven\u0027s work. I will be doing some more though to add lights to other things like docking ports and possibly antennas. \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159391-shotgunninja/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159391\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159391-shotgunninja/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ShotgunNinja\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-14T00:37:29Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2016 12:37  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Benji13\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShotgunNinja","CreatedById":159391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T00:51:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHold on. Those hitchhiker lights are already in Ven Stock Revamp and I never noticed them \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u00A0What your mod change, eg: in that screenshot what is different?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have a minor suggestion: do not use the \u0026gt;\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003E\u0027 \u003C/strong\u003E\u0026lt; character\u00A0in the directory name. Just use BenjisLightupPods.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-14T03:14:14Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2016 03:14  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by ShotgunNinja\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T02:41:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159391-shotgunninja/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159391\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159391-shotgunninja/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ShotgunNinja\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Just added a license to the download\u00A0as well as putting the license into the description on curse.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShotgunNinja","CreatedById":159391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T03:29:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNicely done. I have a question: does this add a toggable light to the stock (as in not Ven)\u00A0pods? Or is this more like a repack with only the light-related parts of Ven? I\u0027m asking because I can\u0027t figure that out from the screenshots. Anyway, looking forward for the antenna lights!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T03:38:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI didn\u0027t include any of the added parts that Vens revamp has. This\u00A0adds the lights on/light off toggle to all the stock parts and also adds new textures to them. Exactly the same as space plane\u00A0parts. \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159391-shotgunninja/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022159391\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/159391-shotgunninja/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@ShotgunNinja\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nedit: Light up antennas could be a while away as I want to do light up docking ports first and I\u0027m not that experienced at modding.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: I\u0027ll add some more screenshots as well, some showing the right click menu.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-14T03:48:53Z\u0022 title=\u002205/14/2016 03:48  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 14, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Benji13\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ShotgunNinja","CreatedById":159391,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T03:54:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDocking ports lights will be very useful. For some strange reasons I always end up docking in shadow...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benji13","CreatedById":162932,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-14T04:26:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222580688\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463198070\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022159391\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ShotgunNinja\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, ShotgunNinja said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDocking ports lights will be very useful. For some strange reasons I always end up docking in shadow...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSame here. Been playing ksp for ages. Not once docked in the light.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Stone Blue","CreatedById":77721,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-01-17T12:14:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust in case anyone is ever looking for this, the link in the \u003Cabbr title=\u00221. Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it. 2. Overpowered. A part or mechanic that upsets game balance by being too powerful.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E is broke since Curse changed its format.\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nHere\u0027s a current link that still works:\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.curseforge.com/kerbal/ksp-mods/benjis-light-up-command-pods\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://www.curseforge.com/kerbal/ksp-mods/benjis-light-up-command-pods\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}